      "title": "President will ONLY communicate through the Speaker",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); President Gotabaya Rajapaksa will only communicate through the speaker, said the President\u2019s Office on Monday (11).",
        "A statement said that announcements made by the speaker alone, must be considered as official statements from the President."
